  • java.lang.Object

    public class NumberMappedOHLCSeriesCollection
extends Object
implements org.jfree.data.xy.OHLCDataset, INumberMappedCollection
    Wrapper for OHLCSeriesCollection to map timestamp values to x-axis numeric indexes.
